text: Louise Elisabeth Coldenhoff (22 March 1935 â€“ 7 February 2021) was an Indonesian Navy colonel. She was one of the first 12 members of the Navy Women's Corps. She later was head of the Jakarta Regional Office of the Ministry of Education and Culture under Governor Soeprapto from 1983 to 1987. Coldenhoff died at a Central Jakarta hospital on 7 February 2021, aged 85. ==References== Category:1935 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Indonesian military people
